It’s in client.java

if (objectID == ####)
{
teleportToX = ####;
teleportToY = ####;
sendMessage("...");
}

Delta/DDS Speced:

if (objectID == ####)
{
toX = ####;
toY = ####;
sM("...");
}

Or use a case…

case ####:
teleportToX = ####;
teleportToY = ####;
sendMessage("...");
break;

Delta/DDS Speced:

case ####:
toX = ####;
toY = ####:
sM("...");
break;
